sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時個個都有 無果d 跟本好難同人爭<br />\n雖然護士都應該呢世都唔會夠人<br />\n但總有d 位比較搶手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:47:19.000Z","msg":"這自願計劃是為他日法定專科護士註冊做準備，其實這是護理業發展必須的，因為香港專科護士的英文就是advanced practice nurse(APN)，國際標準的APN就是法定獨立診療處方執業，如果護士沒有法定權力去做社會和client認同是重要的判斷，護士根本不是專業。"},{"pid":"fbcd672f0a814fa054e581d2fad2c8939399f280","tid":2387114,"uid":26529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"連perfusionist都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57d6cd420411eacf7485a6583fe5468eac27a37","tid":2387114,"uid":342891,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fbcd672f0a814fa054e581d2fad2c8939399f280","tid":2387114,"uid":26529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"連perfusionist都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:02:59.000Z","msg":"其實連wound都冇，我都相當擔心。希望surgical可以拆番開。<br />\n<br />\n冇理由一個perfusionist或者wound ostomy specialist 的專科係&rdquo;surgical&rdquo;吧"},{"pid":"aa8e5abdecc4b2f517a723636c862e6016b0bd88","tid":2387114,"uid":153811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0656e95c80696c3031c400bb042c67ae995eb5","tid":2387114,"uid":334982,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:34:54.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦，醫生霸權唔會讓搵食權出黎<br />\n<br />\n比你班護狗可以開醫生紙，開藥<br />\n<br />\n仲點係診所番三個鐘就月入廿萬<br />\n<br />\n諗都唔洗諗"},{"pid":"a8c74c13483bde3aaaa8a0e23c1b6eee55c139e9","tid":2387114,"uid":342891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa8e5abdecc4b2f517a723636c862e6016b0bd88","tid":2387114,"uid":153811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:50:59.000Z","msg":"現有的權力根本是有問題，外國五十多年期已經有法定護士獨立診療處方執業，大量研究証實治療效果至少等於甚至優於醫生"},{"pid":"a00f60ae2a93b314bf10445b274b6fc906d63276","tid":2387114,"uid":342891,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb0656e95c80696c3031c400bb042c67ae995eb5","tid":2387114,"uid":334982,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:34:54.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦，醫生霸權唔會讓搵食權出黎<br />\n<br />\n比你班護狗可以開醫生紙，開藥<br />\n<br />\n仲點係診所番三個鐘就月入廿萬<br />\n<br />\n諗都唔洗諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:53:56.000Z","msg":"事情當然不會容易，不過為了香港人和護士的共同利益我們會盡全力推倒醫生的不道德霸權，知其不可為而為之，因為這是應該做的事。"},{"pid":"8bf19dd114f80a639fa0f9c86f88d56f95f83721","tid":2387114,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:02:39.000Z","msg":"不如順手推埋醫藥分家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1436c3b4e3750aad8b720e0d618eccd61140de","tid":2387114,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8bf19dd114f80a639fa0f9c86f88d56f95f83721","tid":2387114,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:02:39.000Z","msg":"不如順手推埋醫藥分家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:25:16.000Z","msg":"贊成，醫護分家，醫藥分家，所有醫療專業都應該獨立。"},{"pid":"946f0f710690b882c3f42853c0ec768cd2729190","tid":2387114,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:02:57.000Z","msg":"即係 fellowship la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b9ccdcd26efc31fbf8225092cdc09e9fb393c1","tid":2387114,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df1436c3b4e3750aad8b720e0d618eccd61140de","tid":2387114,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8bf19dd114f80a639fa0f9c86f88d56f95f83721","tid":2387114,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:02:39.000Z","msg":"不如順手推埋醫藥分家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:25:16.000Z","msg":"贊成，醫護分家，醫藥分家，所有醫療專業都應該獨立。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:29:25.000Z","msg":"分完 啲藥又貴左"},{"pid":"2d56117e06dc09be1ce09ef3774583b22098c971","tid":2387114,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"咪又係要玩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34cac7c07cf2f6bf170f3cee97793175c241506","tid":2387114,"uid":141435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d56117e06dc09be1ce09ef3774583b22098c971","tid":2387114,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"咪又係要玩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:58:26.000Z","msg":"唔好咁酸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}